column2: SB Plays Return of the Obra Dinn
SB Plays Return of the Obra Dinn 01 - Let's Investigate
column7:
Let's just hope I don't actually need to know anything about history. Or ships. Or insurance.

Return of the Obra Dinn is described by developer Lucas Pope (best known as the developer of the indie hit Papers, Please) as "An Insurance Adventure with Minimal Color". I don't know much more about it than that, so come and join me as I figure out exactly what that might mean.
